CatDescriptText: Other strikers are carrying signs that read, "On Strike Soho Board Unfair to Local 230..." and "Organized Labor Contributes 40% To Chest Funds, Soho Tries To Bust Unions, Local 230...".
TitMainTitle: Soho Tire workers on strike, picketing with signs that read "We Want Soho Board To Bargain In Good Faith And Arbitrate Our Wage Issue, Local 230, G.C.E.O.C. - C.I.O."
